    • Constructor Detail

      • ManualFieldPolicy

        public ManualFieldPolicy(IClassHierarchy cha,
                         java.util.regex.Pattern refinePattern)
        Parameters:
        refinePattern - a pattern for detecting which match edges to refine. If the declaring class of the field related to the match edge matches the pattern, the match edge will be refined. For example, the pattern Pattern.compile("Ljava/util") will cause all fields of classes in the java.util package to be refined.
